:: Beginning {"position":"800,300","size":"100,100"}
The young knight stole a horse and rode off into the night, determined to find the real criminal and bring them to justice. But as he traveled, he heard rumors of a powerful and evil sorcerer known as the Flame Keeper, who was wreaking havoc on the world.
The young knight knew that he had to stop the Flame Keeper before it was too late. He set off on a perilous journey, facing many dangers along the way. He crossed treacherous mountains, fought off dangerous creatures, and navigated dark forests.


