:: Castle {"position":"800,800","size":"100,100"}
The Fire Keeper rose from his throne, the air around him shimmering with heat. With a roar, he unleashed a torrent of flames, engulfing the throne room in a swirling inferno. The knight dodged and weaved through the flames, the Master Sword's magic protecting the knight from the blistering heat.
The knight pressed on, striking with precision and speed, the Master Sword leaving a trail of sparks in its wake. The Fire Keeper retaliated, conjuring a vortex of fireballs that rained down upon the knight. The knight skillfully deflected the fireballs, the blade's enchantment dispersing the flames upon contact.

