:: Cell {"position":"800,100","size":"100,100"}
Once upon a time, in a kingdom far, far away, there was a young knight with no name. He was an orphan, taken in by the kingdom's knights and trained in the art of combat. However, the young knight was framed for a crime he did not commit and was thrown into the kingdom's darkest dungeon.
Despite the hopelessness of his situation, the young knight never lost hope. He spent his days planning his escape, determined to clear his name and restore his honor.
One day, the young knight saw his chance. A guard had forgotten to lock his cell properly, and he was able to break free. He quickly gathered his belongings and snuck out of the dungeon, avoiding the guards and making his way to the kingdom's stables.

